reviewText:
I first rented this movie on VHS years ago. It was titled " Emmanuel Around The World ". If you saw Emmanuel in America and remember the part

where she was covertly snapping photos, explicit photos I might add, then

I'll tell you there is more of same here. One problem, It wouldn't play on

two out of three machines I tried it on. I have two DVD-RW / VCR combos and a DVD player/ VCR combo. It wouldn't play on the first two, but did play on the last one with nary a problem. This a Russian made import and the sound wasn't all that great. The video quality was ok though.

Again Emmanuel goes undercover,( both figuratively and literally ) to expose a white slavery ring. This movie follows those exploits, with all the nudity and sex that one come expect from this series. An OK time waster. Charlie S. Richmond Va.
